premise_source_doc_sentence: The Star Wars space opera media franchise began with Lucas 's 1977 film Star Wars , which is set `` a long time ago in a galaxy far , far away '' and chronicles the attempt by the characters Luke Skywalker , Princess Leia , Han Solo , and the Wookiee Chewbacca -- assisted by the Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and the droids C-3PO and R2-D2 -- to thwart the evil plans of Sith Lord Darth Vader and the Galactic Empire .
